Name: optic nerve astrocytoma
Definition: A movement disorder that causes involuntary tremors

Name: childhood optic nerve glioma
Definition: A cell type benign neoplasm that is composed_of epithelial tissue in which tumor cells form glands or glandlike structures.
Synonym: glioma of the pediatric visual pathway
